com.interpss.core.aclf

Interface AclfGen

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AcscGen, DStabGen, Dynamic3PGen, Steady3PGen
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AclfGenImpl, AcscGenImpl, DStabGenImpl, Dynamic3PGenImpl, Steady3PGenImpl

    public interface AclfGen
extends NameTag
    A representation of the model object 'Gen'. ACLF contribution generator model class

    The following features are supported:

    • Gen
    • Desired Volt Mag
    • QGen Limit
    • PGen Limit
    • VLimit
    • Rated Voltage
    • Remote VControl Bus Id
    • Mva Base
    • Source Z
    • Xfr Z
    • Xfr Tap
    • Mvar Control PFactor
    • Mw Control PFactor
    • Parent Bus
    See Also:
    AclfPackage.getAclfGen()
